short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bring the fierce and graceful Yor Forger, also known as the Thorn Princess, to life on your new tab with this dynamic live wallpaper

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Unleash the power and beauty of Yor Forger, the deadly assassin known as the Thorn Princess, every time you open a new tab. This stunning live wallpaper showcases Yor in her assassin persona, poised to strike with her deadly skills. As a loving wife and mother in Spy X Family, she leads a double life that combines elegance and lethal force. Whether she's in her role as a protective mother or executing a mission as the Thorn Princess, this wallpaper highlights her incredible strength and complex character.

For fans of Spy X Family who adore Yor's ability to balance her family life with her assassin duties, this wallpaper will add excitement and beauty to your browsing experience.

Key Features
🗡️ Thorn Princess Live Wallpaper: A dynamic display of Yor Forger in her iconic assassin form, ready for action.
🔍 Google Search Bar: Easily search the web with Yor’s fierce presence in the background.
🕒 Clock & Date Display: Track time while immersed in the intensity of Yor’s world.
🔗 Customizable Site Shortcuts: Add quick shortcuts to your favorite websites for easy access.
🔗 Quick Access Links: Manage your extensions easily with “Remove Extension” and “More Extensions” links at the bottom left corner.
With the Thorn Princess Spy X Family Live Wallpaper, your new tab becomes an exciting blend of beauty, strength, and thrilling action—perfect for fans of this fierce and unforgettable character!
